178
00:18:13,659 --> 00:18:19,659
<i>Bütün hislerim beni terk edeli
on sekiz yıl geçti.</i>

179
00:18:48,827 --> 00:18:50,818
<i>Evet, baba.</i>

180
00:18:59,215 --> 00:19:02,975
<b>4 NİSAN</b>

181
